Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.17,0:00:07.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说回到王都…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.26,0:00:13.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.22,0:00:16.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋居然挟持梅尔蒂王女做人质
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.93,0:00:18.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人质
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.56,0:00:21.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骑士们正义站在我们这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.27,0:00:23.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,审判盾之恶魔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.19,0:00:27.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于被当成恶魔了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.07,0:00:29.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉芙塔莉雅菲洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.80,0:01:00.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撤撤退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.27,0:01:06.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要追吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.48,0:01:07.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.77,0:01:10.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅尔没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.95,0:02:58.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,13 盾の惡魔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.20,0:04:15.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小梅尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.87,0:04:18.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尚文大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.66,0:04:20.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那边怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.58,0:04:25.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,城镇和村庄里也传播着被窜改过的影像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.00,0:04:27.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随便接近恐怕会有危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.42,0:04:29.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.96,0:04:31.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.93,0:04:38.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要在我们面前杀掉第2王女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.10,0:04:42.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回答我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.52,0:04:45.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没义务回答恶魔的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.69,0:04:53.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是三勇教的标志呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.15,0:04:55.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三勇教?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.78,0:04:59.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是祟拜剑与枪与弓的梅洛马格国教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.24,0:05:02.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来那个教会里也有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.50,0:05:05.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盾以外的三勇教吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.50,0:05:10.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威胁我国体制的罪行就让你亲自偿还吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.13,0:05:14.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那到底是在说什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.26,0:05:18.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不太懂反正是国王的馊主意吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.30,0:05:22.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪这家伙的老爸我们现在寸步难行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.48,0:05:26.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是父亲的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.90,0:05:28.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是谁的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.36,0:05:32.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕是姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.53,0:05:36.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她来杀掉你夺走第一继承人的地位吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.78,0:05:42.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但当时袭击你的是国王直属骑士吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.83,0:05:46.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把你父亲当成同党也很合理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.50,0:05:49.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竞是他们两个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.29,0:05:54.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定会推说这件事全是盾之恶魔干的以此来陷害我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.22,0:05:57.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲不会做这种事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.84,0:05:59.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么这么肯定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.55,0:06:02.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为父亲他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.27,0:06:07.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种父亲没必要包庇吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.10,0:06:10.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是这样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.65,0:06:11.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小梅尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.32,0:06:13.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是这样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.28,0:06:16.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么就不能理解呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.49,0:06:20.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和父亲现在都不应该闹矛盾啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.53,0:06:24.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再和父亲谈谈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.37,0:06:26.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尚文大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.58,0:06:34.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这样下去没脸面对母亲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.63,0:06:39.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别哭小梅尔菲洛在呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.44,0:06:52.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我决定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.90,0:06:58.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主人欢迎回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.57,0:07:06.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说我们要离开这个国家你怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.21,0:07:11.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要再回王都和父亲…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.33,0:07:15.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别现在回去你只会被杀掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.26,0:07:19.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果愿意跟着我们我们保护你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.22,0:07:22.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这点我还能和你保证
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.51,0:07:27.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小梅尔一起走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.43,0:07:32.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在黎明前出发准备好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.98,0:07:35.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尚文大人目的地是哪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.19,0:07:38.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经决定好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.38,0:07:55.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.59,0:07:59.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法吧拉着马车不能翻山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.97,0:08:02.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这件事解决了我们就回来取
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.30,0:08:06.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对?绝对会回来吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.13,0:08:42.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里休息一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.76,0:08:47.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二王女你没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.31,0:08:52.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎累了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.19,0:08:58.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尚文大人为什么把目的地换成席德威鲁特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.07,0:09:01.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过是戒备程度的差距罢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.82,0:09:06.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然那么戒备就说明那是个对他们不利的国家吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.37,0:09:09.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定是个逃跑的好去处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.95,0:09:11.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.84,0:09:23.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.01,0:09:30.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我问一个问题你和父亲之间发生了什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.23,0:09:36.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.69,0:09:41.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,母亲一直在说要好好对待盾之勇者大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.99,0:09:46.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来我没听你提过你妈的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.74,0:09:50.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,母亲是这个国家的女王哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.74,0:09:51.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女王?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.83,0:09:54.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是女王比父亲更伟大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.87,0:09:57.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女王权力更大吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.67,0:10:00.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为梅洛马格是女王世袭的国家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.55,0:10:05.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么那国王是入赘的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.55,0:10:07.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么好笑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.30,0:10:09.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,副拽样的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.85,0:10:11.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,入赘也没关系吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.60,0:10:12.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然是入赘的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.44,0:10:17.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.00,0:10:35.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边没找到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.83,0:10:39.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们应该还没走远仔细找
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.60,0:11:01.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里也不行吗往回走一点吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.53,0:11:16.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了在那边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.50,0:11:19.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被发现了吗能跑吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.08,0:11:24.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,口气跑到那块岩石附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.40,0:11:47.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们无处可逃已经被包围了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.19,0:11:51.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放弃无谓的抵抗放了梅尔蒂王女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.07,0:11:55.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么放不放的我又没抓她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.41,0:11:58.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,装什么傻我们有证据
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.91,0:12:02.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位勇者正如各位所见我没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.67,0:12:05.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盾之勇者保护了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.42,0:12:10.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等尚文不是诱拐了梅尔蒂王女吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.38,0:12:15.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此次骚动背后有巨大的阴谋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.76,0:12:19.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了让他保护我这是我主动要求的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.06,0:12:21.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保护你?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.89,0:12:26.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盾之勇者绑架我能有什么好处呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.11,0:12:28.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女王说过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.57,0:12:35.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在正是互相携手一起团结击退灾难的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.45,0:12:40.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个世界已经容不得无谓的争斗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.58,0:12:43.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请放下武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.58,0:12:47.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她说得没错这是阴谋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.05,0:12:51.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来我会把自己知道的说出来所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.51,0:12:53.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能听
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.72,0:12:57.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盾之恶魔有洗脑之盾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.76,0:13:03.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那面可恨的盾拥有只要交流就能洗脑对方的能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.39,0:13:06.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么谁会相信这种谎言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.98,0:13:09.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据三勇教会的调查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.11,0:13:14.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大约一个月前各地出现了崇拜盾的邪教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.03,0:13:16.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是三勇教吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.32,0:13:23.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盾之恶魔自称神鸟圣人到处洗脑众人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.46,0:13:24.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.17,0:13:31.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可怜的梅尔蒂已经彻底被盾之恶魔洗脑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.38,0:13:37.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊那么拉芙塔莉雅和菲洛也被尚文…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.22,0:13:40.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的我们没有被洗脑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.06,0:13:44.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说到底如果盾有这个力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.14,0:13:46.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事情就不会变成现在这样吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.48,0:13:48.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是也不能证明没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.81,0:13:51.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能拿出让我们信服的证据吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.65,0:13:57.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尚文先把第二王女交给我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.57,0:14:00.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们保证不会加害她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.91,0:14:07.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确如果可以不用战斗的话·
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.88,0:14:09.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样或许不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.80,0:14:14.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炼大人说得没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.67,0:14:18.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅尔蒂的人身安全是最重要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.85,0:14:28.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来一起回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.52,0:14:32.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行回去会被杀掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.91,0:14:42.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.12,0:14:48.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了救救我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.26,0:15:01.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炼很感谢你的建议不过不能把第二王女交给这个女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.14,0:15:04.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.77,0:15:13.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么呢梅尔蒂是我重要的妹妹我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.48,0:15:18.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就这么想要第一继承人的位置甚至不惜杀掉亲妹妹吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.53,0:15:23.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以解除洗脑为借口借机杀掉第二王女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.91,0:15:25.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很像是你会做的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.33,0:15:30.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟已经约好了要保护她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.21,0:15:32.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.13,0:15:34.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.84,0:15:41.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冲过去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.14,0:15:45.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灵气盾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.73,0:15:59.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别想得逞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.60,0:16:34.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经呼叫增援你们逃不掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.36,0:16:39.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿不掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.86,0:16:43.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.03,0:16:45.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放放开我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.78,0:16:48.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒没有力气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.28,0:16:53.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了让菲洛保持天使的外貌我拜托这个国家的炼金术师做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.17,0:16:55.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以力量之源命令你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.54,0:17:00.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解读理之力以水之刃将其斩断
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.21,0:17:03.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中级水刃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.68,0:17:09.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来我会打中放开小菲洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.31,0:17:19.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麦茵小姐你想杀掉梅尔蒂王女吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.98,0:17:22.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是她先出手的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.90,0:17:26.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中级地狱火中级火焰箭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.82,0:17:29.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干什么住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.04,0:17:34.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然无法解开洗脑就只能杀掉她了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.00,0:17:43.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尚文大人梅尔暂时交给您
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.34,0:17:46.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯你离远一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.05,0:17:50.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧愤怒之盾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.22,0:17:54.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.19,0:18:02.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那面盾是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.07,0:18:08.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧对盾之恶魔施以正义的铁锤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.83,0:18:10.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放箭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.59,0:18:24.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.51,0:18:32.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轮到菲洛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.10,0:18:39.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消灭盾之恶魔和其同党
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.44,0:18:43.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.08,0:18:54.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那道光是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.84,0:19:05.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟发生了什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.63,0:19:07.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.55,0:19:10.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这件事背后究竟有什么阴谋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.35,0:19:13.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该能想明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.35,0:19:15.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住尚文
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.91,0:19:34.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.00,0:19:42.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等她是我们的同伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.00,0:19:47.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女王直属秘密谍报部队「影」的一员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.88,0:19:53.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盾之勇者阁下我是初次以这副面貌与您相见是也
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.14,0:19:55.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个口头禅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.10,0:20:00.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请恕我开门见山是也
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.48,0:20:05.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盾之勇者阁下希望您去拜见女王陛下是也
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.48,0:20:07.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,见女王?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.28,0:20:10.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次的事件起因复杂是也
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.36,0:20:13.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果可以希望您能协助我们是也
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.37,0:20:20.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此次的诱拐事件是认为盾阁下会造成威胁的入设计的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.54,0:20:23.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又有麻烦的家伙出现了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.58,0:20:26.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么见女王对我来说有什么好处呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.09,0:20:31.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些等您见到陛下之后就知道了是也
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.18,0:20:40.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女王在的地方和席德威鲁特是反方向吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.85,0:20:44.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二王女你知道这个国家吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.86,0:20:50.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了第二王女你会用魔法吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.32,0:20:53.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这么叫我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.78,0:20:55.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么第二王女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.12,0:20:56.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别叫我第二王女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.49,0:20:58.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.46,0:21:04.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫梅尔蒂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.46,0:21:11.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可盾之勇者一口一个第二王女别把我排除在外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.80,0:21:15.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不也叫我盾之勇者吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.35,0:21:21.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我叫你尚文所以你叫我梅尔蒂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.77,0:21:24.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来叫啊尚文
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.35,0:21:26.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直呼名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.69,0:21:29.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了第二王女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.32,0:21:30.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.07,0:21:32.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅尔蒂这样行了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.78,0:21:34.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再叫一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.87,0:21:38.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再叫一次叫我的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.62,0:21:40.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅尔蒂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.79,0:21:46.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,定要保护我啊还有谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.34,0:21:48.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.25,0:21:52.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.43,0:21:57.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这股味道
